### Get stock details
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/stockssrv/stockset HTTP/1.1

### Post
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/stockssrv/stockset HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{

    "symbol": "SBIN",
    "name": "Kotak Bank",
    "quantity": 10,
    "mktprice": 500,
    "avgprice": 200
}

### Update stock
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/stockssrv/stockset/c68d2648-1822-41e0-9828-757910337d2e HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{

    "quantity": 10
}

### delete stock
DELETE http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/stockssrv/stockset/1164c587-fa47-4bcb-8b51-291ee5f4231a HTTP/1.1

### Get portfolio details
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/stockssrv/holdings HTTP/1.1

